ombine a sample room which develops prototypes and samples in real time.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We have multiple <strong>sample rooms in Italy</strong> for small high-quality productions. We have a commercial representative and business development office for Northern Europe based in Amsterdam. We give style advices and management consultancy for the production of clothing and accessories located in South America.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Our customers are:</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-78 alignnone\" src=\"http://www.puntozeroint.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bottone1.png\" alt=\"bottone1\" width=\"27\" height=\"27\" /> designers who want to create, produce and sell their collections</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-81 alignnone\" src=\"http://www.puntozeroint.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bottone2.png\" alt=\"bottone2\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> leather goods brands that want to develop the production of their collections in other countries</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-80\" src=\"http://www.puntozeroint.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bottone3.png\" alt=\"bottone3\" width=\"27\" height=\"27\" /> clothing brands who want to produce and develop their Private Label of leather goods, accessories and garments</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-82 alignnone\" src=\"http://www.puntozeroint.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bottone4.png\" alt=\"bottone4\" width=\"27\" height=\"27\" /> buying offices seeking for the right sourcing in their production process for their customers</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-83 alignnone\" src=\"http://www.puntozeroint.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/bottone5.png\" alt=\"bottone5\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> companies that need to control production certified Quality on-site.</p>\r\n[galler